[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.367,
    "text": "♪♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.501,
    "endTime": 2.769,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.902,
    "endTime": 7.7410000000000005,
    "text": "♪♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.874,
    "endTime": 9.174,
    "text": "Looks like there's some cleaning up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.309,
    "endTime": 10.744,
    "text": "to do around here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.877,
    "endTime": 12.712,
    "text": "Whoa, Spiderman!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.846,
    "endTime": 14.247,
    "text": "I just noticed that you threw your wrapper"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.381,
    "endTime": 15.515,
    "text": "on the grass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.648,
    "endTime": 17.784,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, I guess I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.917,
    "endTime": 18.985000000000003,
    "text": "It's better for the planet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.119,
    "endTime": 20.387,
    "text": "and for everyone who shares it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.52,
    "endTime": 23.023,
    "text": "if we all clean up after ourselves and don't litter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.156,
    "endTime": 24.857,
    "text": "It reminds me of the time with Miles Morales"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.991,
    "endTime": 26.726,
    "text": "when we had to stop that villain Hobgoblin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.86,
    "endTime": 28.828,
    "text": "from throwing garbage everywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.962,
    "endTime": 30.13,
    "text": "Sure glad we had time to eat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.263,
    "endTime": 31.498,
    "text": "before they opened the new park."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.799,
    "endTime": 34.834,
    "text": "[excited chatter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.968,
    "endTime": 35.568000000000005,
    "text": "[clears throat]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.702,
    "endTime": 36.669,
    "text": "[microphone feedback]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.803,
    "endTime": 38.437,
    "text": "Hi, thank you all for coming to the opening"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.571,
    "endTime": 41.274,
    "text": "of our new city park and playground."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.408,
    "endTime": 43.843,
    "text": "Look at them all having fun together,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.977,
    "endTime": 47.98,
    "text": "when here I am all alone with nothing to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.114,
    "endTime": 50.717,
    "text": "I know how I'll have some fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.85,
    "endTime": 53.42,
    "text": "I'll mess with their good time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.553,
    "endTime": 54.22,
    "text": "[maniacal laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.354,
    "endTime": 56.522,
    "text": "[screaming]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.656,
    "endTime": 59.225,
    "text": "[maniacal laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.359,
    "endTime": 61.661,
    "text": "[dismayed shouts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.795,
    "endTime": 65.397,
    "text": "Spiderman: Hey, what gives? It's raining garbage!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.532,
    "endTime": 69.101,
    "text": "Ah, it's Hobgoblin! Time to swing into action, Spidey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.37,
    "endTime": 73.44,
    "text": "Oops, looks like I missed a spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.573,
    "endTime": 77.577,
    "text": "Just how I like it, nice and dirty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.71,
    "endTime": 79.145,
    "text": "Spiderman: Nothing nice about it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.279,
    "endTime": 80.914,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.047,
    "endTime": 82.315,
    "text": "Looks like you're not going forward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.349,
    "endTime": 84.884,
    "text": "And you're definitely not going back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.018,
    "endTime": 87.887,
    "text": "The only thing worse than one Spidey is two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.021,
    "endTime": 88.721,
    "text": "[frustrated grunt]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.855,
    "endTime": 90.79,
    "text": "[stretching sound]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.924,
    "endTime": 91.491,
    "text": "[snap]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.592,
    "endTime": 95.929,
    "text": "Too bad my glider is stronger than both of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.062,
    "endTime": 99.93299999999999,
    "text": "Here's some garbage. My gift to you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.066,
    "endTime": 102.769,
    "text": "Aw, yuck. He's getting away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.902,
    "endTime": 104.337,
    "text": "Eugh, we're going to have to show him"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.471,
    "endTime": 106.406,
    "text": "he can't trash and run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.64,
    "endTime": 109.642,
    "text": "[maniacal laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.776,
    "endTime": 112.244,
    "text": "You two can't catch me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.378,
    "endTime": 116.116,
    "text": "I wouldn't be so sure. And stop littering!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.249,
    "endTime": 116.982,
    "text": "What should we do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.117,
    "endTime": 118.184,
    "text": "Follow my lead!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.188,
    "text": "[maniacal laughter]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.322,
    "endTime": 123.35600000000001,
    "text": "Gotcha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.49,
    "endTime": 126.192,
    "text": "Uh oh. [screams]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.326,
    "endTime": 127.693,
    "text": "[crash]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.827,
    "endTime": 130.463,
    "text": "It's gonna take more than that to stop me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.465,
    "endTime": 134.901,
    "text": "Well, that's OK. We have a lot more than \"that.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.034,
    "endTime": 136.435,
    "text": "Yeah, we're not going to let you ruin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.569,
    "endTime": 138.438,
    "text": "the new park for everyone, Hobgoblin!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.571,
    "endTime": 141.107,
    "text": "Oh, yeah? Well, see if you can catch me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.241,
    "endTime": 142.675,
    "text": "[angry muttering]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.809,
    "endTime": 143.977,
    "text": "You're not going anywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.11,
    "endTime": 145.61200000000002,
    "text": "[thwack thwack]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.745,
    "endTime": 148.615,
    "text": "Ha! Caught! With the help of our friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.748,
    "endTime": 150.617,
    "text": "Thanks, everyone! We stopped Hobby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.75,
    "endTime": 152.118,
    "text": "Mission accomplished!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.252,
    "endTime": 154.92100000000002,
    "text": "Not yet. There's a lot of cleaning up to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.054,
    "endTime": 156.656,
    "text": "Thanks for nothing, Hobgoblin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.789,
    "endTime": 158.42299999999997,
    "text": "Why did you have to ruin everyone's good time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.558,
    "endTime": 162.095,
    "text": "I guess I felt... left out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.228,
    "endTime": 164.297,
    "text": "So you want to feel included?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.43,
    "endTime": 166.699,
    "text": "I have a feeling I'm not going to like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.867,
    "endTime": 169.402,
    "text": "Wow, look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.536,
    "endTime": 173.673,
    "text": "[laughing and murmuring]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.806,
    "endTime": 175.40800000000002,
    "text": "All those nice people working together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.542,
    "endTime": 177.01,
    "text": "to clean up your trash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.143,
    "endTime": 179.279,
    "text": "Go ahead, Hobgoblin. Time to join in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.412,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "It's only right for you to help"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 182.182,
    "text": "to clean up the mess you made."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.315,
    "endTime": 184.517,
    "text": "You'll definitely feel included now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.651,
    "endTime": 188.75500000000002,
    "text": "[grumbling and disgusted sounds]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.888,
    "endTime": 192.125,
    "text": "Nice job, Hobby. We'll have this place clean in no time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.26,
    "endTime": 195.56099999999998,
    "text": "♪♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.695,
    "endTime": 198.631,
    "text": "[giggling] There! All done!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.765,
    "endTime": 200.767,
    "text": "Good going! See how much nicer everything looks"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.9,
    "endTime": 202.335,
    "text": "when you clean up after yourself?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.468,
    "endTime": 203.703,
    "text": "Mmm hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.836,
    "endTime": 206.27200000000002,
    "text": "And no one will be able to call us litter... \"bugs\", get it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.84,
    "endTime": 209.309,
    "text": "Spidey out!"
  }
]